The Senzo Meyiwa murder trial continues in the High Court in Pretoria. PRETORIA - The Senzo Meyiwa murder trial continues in the High Court in Pretoria. Now this case has had quite a few twists and turns, the most recent being the arrest in court of defence lawyer Malesela Teffo. Five men are accused of killing Meyiwa, a former Bafana Bafana captain and goalkeeper. He was shot dead at the home of his girlfriend, Kelly Khumalo, almost eight years ago.